casebody.data:
Ivan Earl WARREN
v.
Lawrence PARSONS. No. 239P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 15, 2015. Ivan Earl Warren, for Warren, Ivan Earl. Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 14th of July 2015 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Onslow County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of July 2015."
